FROM-------
RUN------Excutes the commands during the build process
EXPOSE----- EXPOSE is used in a Dockerfile to specify the port on which the application inside the container will listen.
CMD-----
_____________________________________________________
RUN → executes during image build

CMD → executes during container start

ENTRYPOINT → executes during container start
__________________________________________________________

| Scenario            | Result                                 |
| ------------------- | -------------------------------------- |
| Multiple CMD        | Last CMD executes                      |
| Multiple ENTRYPOINT | Last ENTRYPOINT executes               |
| ENTRYPOINT + CMD    | ENTRYPOINT runs, CMD acts as arguments |

| Instruction | When it executes          |
| ----------- | ------------------------- |
| RUN         | During **image build**    |
| CMD         | When **container starts** |
| ENTRYPOINT  | When **container starts** |

